unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Printed Ephemera Collection of Government Publications
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Printed Ephemera Collection of Government Publications contains pamphlets and publications from federal governments around the world, publications from United States governmental departments, as well as from US state and municipal governments. The collection ranges in date from 1894-1988. Generally, the countries represented were/are related to communism. For instance there are pamphlets from Cuba, the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, the Democratic Republic of Vietnam, the German Democratic Republic, and the Soviet Union. The US national, state, and municipal files relate primarily to economics, foreign affairs, labor, social security, and unemployment.
